Commentary Text: Mohit Sharma to Christian, out Bowled!! Kaboom! Who says the yorker has gone out of fashion? It never has and it never will. Lovely yorker from Mohit, on the base of off stump and Christian was making room to slam it through cover. Too good a nut for him and he fails to get his bat down in time. Timber it is! DD finish on 166/7. Is it enough? Christian b Mohit Sharma 13(13) [6s-1]

Commentary Text: Mohit Sharma to Chris Morris, 3 runs, comedy of errors! Initially a good stop by Tye, doesn't stop it cleanly as his slide ended up booting it, then Stoinis in the tag team effort nearly overruns the ball. Saves it though and finally, the umpire by mistake signals a boundary before apologizing. Gee! Fuller ball that was hacked away towards deep mid-wicket. Struck it fairly well but good fielding denied him a boundary. They get three though

Commentary Text: Andrew Tye to Rahul Tewatia, out Gambhir Run Out!! Brilliance from Mujeeb! Direct hits are always dangerous and it's proven this time. Slower ball on leg, Tye got away with this delivery as fine leg was up in the ring. Mujeeb was quick to attack the ball and threw down the stumps at the keeper's end in a flash.
